# ─── Ascend API — XP & Level Endpoints ───────────────────────────────────────

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api/v1
@token = REPLACE_WITH_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Get current level and XP
GET {{baseUrl}}/xp/level
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get XP history
GET {{baseUrl}}/xp/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get XP history paginated
GET {{baseUrl}}/xp/history?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
